{"title":"山村即景","authors":["郑成义","晓田","莒南"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村即景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑成义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山里山，弯里弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠柏连荫村口上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村云里藏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村路不用问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜蜂把路引。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——养蜂场，闹盈盈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯尽疑无路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云里打稻声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——新砌梯田层层金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻说放映队进山来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少出村迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着电杆奔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙山上，歌声响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙山上、歌声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少挖塘忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你打土呀，我装筐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对剖竹担软洋洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖一担，又一担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖得池塘深两丈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年春雷一声水满塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比宝镜银亮亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……龙山上，歌声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲤鱼莲花满池塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涵门一开龙摆尾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄谷子堆成山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说龙怒不可犯？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖了龙爪挖龙胆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山谷谷歌声满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖出宝镜照咱好时光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冬夜晚闹喧天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野灯笼一盏盏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是过年提灯会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是社员忙着修梯田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深冬夜晚暗又寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青人流汗湿衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是烤火的火炉旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他们挥镢头舞铁铣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空寒星微光闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地面上火花四处溅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是孩子们放花火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是镢头下去把石翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土滚滚黑土翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层梯田岭上连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今冬多翻几亩地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收图景在眼前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（山东  莒南）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}